formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1)This certificate is being issued on request of M/S. YOGI CORPORATION for RERA
compliance of Project YOGI HEIGHTS and it is based on the books of accounts  maintained by the firm and other records/documents produced before us for our verification and information & explanations provided to us by the partners of the firm and to the best of our knowledge and belief. Also the estimated figures wherever provided herein above are taken as certified by the Engineer/Architect and Partner of the firm.
2) Further, the details provided in the Annexure to this certificate, i.e. calculation of receivables from sales of sold inventory, booking of garages and parkings and valuation of unsold inventory and other details is based on management representation provided to us.
3) Rera bank account for Project Yogi Heights registered with gujRERA was overdraft account and this overdraft account was closed on 02/05/2019 . Hence we have reported rera bank account details ( deposits, withdrawals ) till 02/05/2019.
4) As per on information & explanations provided to us by the partners of the firm this is to inform you that unsecured loans taken from lendors are used for marketing purpose not for construction purpose . Hence interest paid on unsecured loans is considered in calculating Construction Cost Incurred and Paid.
